To save space on the repository, I linked to the datasets

Rifai2011.pdf uses datasets from http://www.iro.umontreal.ca/~lisa/icml2007
basic: smaller subset of MNIST: http://www.iro.umontreal.ca/~lisa/icml2007data/mnist.zip
rot: digits with added random rotation: http://www.iro.umontreal.ca/~lisa/icml2007data/mnist_rotation_new.zip
bg-rand: digits with random noise background: http://www.iro.umontreal.ca/~lisa/icml2007data/mnist_background_images.zip
bg-img: digits with random image background: http://www.iro.umontreal.ca/~lisa/icml2007data/mnist_background_random.zip 
bg-img-rot: digits with rotation and image background: http://www.iro.umontreal.ca/~lisa/icml2007data/mnist_rotation_back_image_new.zip
rect: discriminate between tall and wide rectangles (white on black): http://www.iro.umontreal.ca/~lisa/icml2007data/rectangles.zip
rect-img: discriminate between tall and wide rectangular image on a different background image: http://www.iro.umontreal.ca/~lisa/icml2007data/rectangles_images.zip
